    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247050/extras/1797450b40bd90df2f234abe05a3e93e.avif?t=1737896969\" width=768 height=96 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore Dodd's local museum in this short and sweet, casual and relaxing side-scroller adventure game! Visit various exhibits within the museum's four wings as you:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >talk to various characters around the museum!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >collect stray weevils!</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >clean up the museum!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy the atmosphere!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game itself is meant to be in the style of a simple point-and-click game, but with the approach of a side-scroller character interacting with the environment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247050/extras/fb642ce35c546798cb0cd4dadfc525d3.avif?t=1737896969\" width=768 height=96 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>W/A/S/D</strong> (or your keyboard equivalent)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >or</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arrow Keys</p>",
